metadata.name: LlamaBoost (Gold)
metadata.description: This LlamaBoost was originally known as LlamaPass. The LlamaBoost is essentially a powerup for a Llamaverse NFT. This powerup includes amplified $SPIT Generation and other benefits. You must own a Llamaverse to be able to use the utility of this boost. The Silver boost generates less $SPIT than the gold boost. Learn more on our Discord and Twitter!
